  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Decision:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To support the project timeline and requirements, we will go with Solution 1. Once we make the exchange and linking properly, it will be easy for the future China projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Solution1: With both CART and China project in DOORS classic (DOORS exchange):"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Pros:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Control is now completely with project"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Cons:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Complex structure",
        "Needs DOORs exchange and need to run script",
        "Need inspection review to make sure links are established properly"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/2488263286/CnConvPf_Traceability.png?version=66&modificationDate=1679880216000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Safety Traceability Overview/CnConvPf_Traceability.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Solution 2: With CART in DNG and China project in DOORS classic (using specified by):"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Pros:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Simple and less work",
        "Project can concentrate only on Config part.",
        "No big linking and inspection review effort for PF framework"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Cons:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "PF part control is completely with CART"
      ]
    },
    {
